HEADWORD: Restiness
<hw>Rest"i*ness</hw> <pr>(r?st`⟦icr⟧*n?s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
quality or state of being resty; sluggishness.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The snake by <qex>restiness</qex> and lying still all winter.</q>
